          img.img-responsive(asset-src="images/yeoman-logo.png", alt="Yeoman")

  //-  features
  a#features(du-smooth-scroll)
  section#services.slice.color1
    .container
      .row
        .col-xs-12
          h1.center Features
          h2.subTitle Smart hosting for cutting edge web apps
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-cloud-flash.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 Automatic CDN Deployment
              p
                | Client assets automatically deployed to a global CDN for lightning fast downloads with compression and aggressive cache headers.
        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-cog-alt.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 API Integration
              p
                | Intelligent service proxy allows injecting access keys and caching of API responses. Backend not ready yet? Configure our API mocks so you can stay full speed ahead.
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-shuffle.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 Split test like a pro
              p
                | Not sure how users will react to your app’s latest version? Split your traffic with a simple slider and watch the results in real-time.
        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-terminal.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 Developer friendly tools
              p
                | Grunt and Gulp plugins that integrate cleanly into a streamlined modern workflow. Deploy a new version to production with just a few keystrokes.
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-network.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 Works with the web
              p
                | Rich interactivity of a single page app with the discoverability and reach of the web. Custom SSL domains, SEO snapshots, and HTML5 pushState all included.
        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-lock-empty.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 Built-in Security
              p
                | Authenticate users with OAuth. Enforce SSL with the click of a box. Keep sensitive keys on the server and out of your JavaScript.
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-block.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 Goodbye test environment
              p
                | With Aerobatic’s simulator mode, run your front-end changes locally, and the rest of your app in the cloud. Preview changes and test in a fully integrated environment that exactly emulates production.

        .col-sm-6
          .row.boxFeature
            .col-xs-3
              i.icon-code.iconBig
            .col-xs-9
              h2 Use the libraries you love
              p
                | Aerobatic is a platform, not a framework. Build your app with AngularJS, Ember, Backbone, Bootstrap, jQuery, and whatever next best thing comes along.
